OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with some clear spells.
OL,7,FOvernight we will likely see mist and
OL,8,Flow cloud form, with perhaps some
OL,9,Fdrizzle over higher ground. In the
OL,10,Fearly hours, spells of rain may push
OL,11,Finto parts of Cumbria. Feeling warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA mostly dry, bright and
OL,14,Fvery warm day across the south of
OL,15,Fregion. Further north, turning
OL,16,Fincreasingly cloudy with some rain in
OL,17,FCumbria and perhaps parts of
OL,18,FLancashire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
