OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFurther
OL,6,Frain possible on Friday, especially in
OL,7,Fthe north. Becoming drier and brighter
OL,8,Fthis weekend, though still a few
OL,9,Fshowers at first. Warm on Saturday and
OL,10,Frather hot by Sunday.
